lthough he promises not to overdo it during the bachelor party, things get out of control."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.nomanchesfrida.com","overview":"Zequi y Lucy están a punto de casarse. A pesar de que él promete no excederse durante la despedida de soltero, las cosas se salen de control."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"노 만체스 프리다 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"No Manches Frida 2: Paraíso Destruído","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Quando o, aparentemente, reformado ex-presidiário Zequi está prestes a se casar com o amor de sua vida, a adorável e nerd Lucy, o nervosismo do dia do casamento se transforma em um fiasco total e Lucy decide não casar mais. Ao mesmo tempo, a escola, está prestes a ser fechada, caso não ganhem o torneio de escolas. Será que eles vão conseguir ganhar o torneio e Zequi reconquistar Lucy?"},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zequi y Lucy están a punto de casarse. A pesar de que él promete no excederse durante la despedida de soltero, las cosas se salen de control."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Не запятнай Фриду 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Уголовник Зеки стал честным человеком и собирается жениться, но всё идёт не по плану."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"学校整蛊联盟2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zequi úgy szeretné visszanyerni álmai nőjének szívét, hogy megpróbálja győzelemre vinni az iskola röplabdacsapatát."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Wanneer de ogenschijnlijk hervormde ex-gevangene Zequi op het punt staat te trouwen met de liefde van zijn leven, de lieve nerdy Lucy, veranderen de kriebels op de trouwdag in een regelrecht fiasco en roept Lucy het af. Ondertussen komt de school diep in de problemen en gaat de bende naar het water om deel te nemen aan het toernooi van hun leven. Als ze eenmaal aan zee zijn, komt Lucy haar middelbare schoolliefde Mario tegen, coach van de tegenstander en Zequi merkt dat hij een rivaal is in meer dan één competitie. Nu moet hij alles uit de kast halen om zijn luidruchtige kinderen in te schakelen, Lucy terug te winnen, en voor het geval dat nog niet genoeg was, de school te redden van sluiting door Frida High naar de overwinning te leiden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":375794,"adult":false,"title":"No manches, Frida","video":false,"overview":"After being released from prison, Zequi, a bank robber, sets out to recover money buried by his accomplice; but is horrified to learn that a high school gymnasium is now over the site where the loot is hidden.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3742,"vote_count":936,"poster_path":"/6HfyXfIEywLa2HvcswKi44dDKxL.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-02","vote_average":7.684,"backdrop_path":"/3z8cveYwdIz2IZRhm6cHu8f2HRT.jpg","original_title":"No manches, Frida","original_language":"es"},{"id":675024,"adult":false,"title":"The Exorcism of Carmen Farias","video":false,"overview":"Carmen, a brave journalist, discovers soon after her mother's death that she has inherited her grandma's house. She decides to move there without knowing it hides dark secrets.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3083,"vote_count":126,"poster_path":"/uoTPjx07dxTrC1g3dYeaS2WNVGL.jpg","release_date":"2021-05-05","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/zm2kMjiz0u6qdn2XKbEbQkDiltN.jpg","original_title":"El Exorcismo de Carmen Farías","original_language":"es"},{"id":554753,"adult":false,"title":"Mirreyes vs Godínez","video":false,"overview":"A group of yuppies fight over a group of office stooges for the control of a shoe factory.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7825,"vote_count":114,"poster_path":"/bwvgQmyALdiSmLtyxkB9KPG2zdE.jpg","release_date":"2019-01-25","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/pow8TNWeyv1ygbadxZeo9O48dgt.jpg","original_title":"Mirreyes contra Godínez","original_language":"es"},{"id":84354,"adult":false,"title":"Young and Wild","video":false,"overview":"Daniela, raised in the bosom of a strict Evangelical family and recently unmasked as a fornicator by her shocked parents, struggles to find her own path to spiritual harmony.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6581,"vote_count":152,"poster_path":"/ixTyxtsK6W63jrWjixczyeJSex2.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-29","vote_average":6.263,"backdrop_path":"/7kJ92zLRs7ZJDQU1tVdvQGMfksb.jpg","original_title":"Joven y alocada","original_language":"es"},{"id":346034,"adult":false,"title":"3 Idiotas","video":false,"overview":"A group of friends embark on an adventure to find a classmate from university who disappeared without a trace on graduation day.","genre_ids":[10751,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5779,"vote_count":127,"poster_path":"/hZB9NvNLcxdmoiAh58ZfG8vdXjf.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-02","vote_average":7.63,"backdrop_path":"/73icc1rjNGZwuAa9Ife6frwHQnN.jpg","original_title":"3 Idiotas","original_language":"es"},{"id":547590,"adult":false,"title":"El Chicano","video":false,"overview":"A pair of twin brothers from East L.A. choose to live their lives differently and end up on opposite sides of the law.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4639,"vote_count":86,"poster_path":"/6LSJL2KHUAxSjDTWA5V5Cr7sNNd.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-03","vote_average":6.581,"backdrop_path":"/uTtsYLaC9b8joDKy4YGsMxfo3cp.jpg","original_title":"El Chicano","original_language":"en"},{"id":526811,"adult":false,"title":"Simple Passion","video":false,"overview":"A man and a woman are brought together by chance for several months. He is younger than she is, married, Russian, officially a diplomat stationed in Paris. She is a beautiful teacher and researcher, with her feet firmly on the ground. The film follows the evolution of their love, from the beginning to end.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0227,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/gbecuqHDcF8MyllcOBS4YO9oJBz.jpg","release_date":"2021-01-14","vote_average":5.647,"backdrop_path":"/5IETLw4XVLeN8tdWGh11TmJvyUn.jpg","original_title":"Passion simple","original_language":"fr"},{"id":16710,"adult":false,"title":"Meet the Browns","video":false,"overview":"A single mother living in inner city Chicago, Brenda has been struggling for years to make ends meet and keep her three kids off the street. When she's laid off with no warning, she starts losing hope for the first time - until a letter arrives announcing the death of a father she's never met. Desperate for any kind of help, Brenda takes her family to Georgia for the funeral, but nothing could have prepared her for the Browns, her father's fun-loving, crass Southern clan. In a small-town world full of long afternoons and country fairs, Brenda struggles to get to know the family she never knew existed... and finds a brand new romance that just might change her life.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6401,"vote_count":110,"poster_path":"/61qE0TunNdJiPELBdywMlpvZXDB.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-21","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/cOuWAiDW2n9c1NYlODMo7lZejZj.jpg","original_title":"Meet the Browns","original_language":"en"},{"id":40829,"adult":false,"title":"Shaolin Wooden Men","video":false,"overview":"Little Mute is an orphan traumatized into silence by the death of his father at the hands of a vicious fighting master. Living at the Shaolin monastery, he befriends a dangerous prisoner who teaches him a secret form of deadly kung fu. Seeing his intense determination, other masters share the wisdom of the Gliding Snake and Drunken Master techniques. In one of the most exciting fight scenes ever filmed, Little Mute must run the gauntlet of the famous 108 wooden men in an extreme test of skill and endurance. But if he becomes a master, will he use his unmatched force for redemption or revenge?","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0058,"vote_count":134,"poster_path":"/nNeXr9PRv8m83BjfL4K6wP5oPZq.jpg","release_date":"1976-10-10","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/fpaElIjywDDP7WWfS6pyi4qMxHz.jpg","original_title":"少林木人巷","original_language":"zh"},{"id":295237,"adult":false,"title":"The Assault","video":false,"overview":"After a cheerleader is sexually assaulted by the high school football team, she must overcome her shame and use the evidence gathered from the subsequent social media firestorm to piece together the night that she can't remember in her fight for justice. Based on the true story of the Steubenville, Ohio rape case.","genre_ids":[9648,80,18,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8479,"vote_count":78,"poster_path":"/ztyBW1fC7oRrxNdrZsZztcGkvs4.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-20","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eq0N54GnErEcTJtTWu7UOzqfKPp.jpg","original_title":"The Assault","original_language":"en"},{"id":40661,"adult":false,"title":"The Redemption: Kickboxer 5","video":false,"overview":"Kickboxing champion Matt Reeves witnesses the murder of his friend Johnny. While investigating the crime, he learns that a Mr. Negaal in South Africa has founded a new kickboxing association and does not leave international champions much of a chance. Johnny had to pay with his life when he did not want to join. Neegal seems to kill everybody who is in his way especially David Sloan from the previous Kickboxer films. Matt is on his own now, but suddenly finds an unexpected ally.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5079,"vote_count":93,"poster_path":"/oPEaXVR6Ji7c8MkvGKuQP3ZKc5e.jpg","release_date":"1995-08-01","vote_average":4.866,"backdrop_path":"/rLeDU3gRKDpzrZ9hEIvaIwHijyt.jpg","original_title":"The Redemption: Kickboxer 5","original_language":"en"},{"id":245527,"adult":false,"title":"Convict","video":false,"overview":"Set in the dark and old Parramatta prison built by the original convicts our lead character Ray a war veteran finds himself serving 18 months for manslaughter after defending his fiance. He soon realizes that the prison boss has it in for him and does everything possible to break Ray even going after his fiance.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.385,"vote_count":120,"poster_path":"/mnvkok7eVau9Fg8BMDuwmk8JCZw.jpg","release_date":"2014-01-23","vote_average":6.508,"backdrop_path":"/f3rd6o0EQ0TnZsVtS1SD1k580Dh.jpg","original_title":"Convict","original_language":"en"},{"id":517929,"adult":false,"title":"Fog City","video":false,"overview":"A group of friends seal themselves inside a secluded Cape Cod vacation home after a mysterious orange fog leaks from an old nearby factory. Once trapped, they quickly learn there is no escape.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7875,"vote_count":52,"poster_path":"/isewxmxthIUrmPpGHQQlIuOid3s.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-20","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/akwjg4reniSZY8tBItXPwBlZQS2.jpg","original_title":"Fog City","original_language":"en"},{"id":586602,"adult":false,"title":"Papá Youtuber","video":false,"overview":"A family dad with no technology knowledge is fired by his new boss, a young millennial. In desperation to don't lose his home and after learning that his wife is pregnant, he decides to become a YouTuber, for what he will need the help of his two misunderstood kids.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1117,"vote_count":34,"poster_path":"/qGgcGtgNGXAEdyuj7o6JttQZvy3.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-11","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/dJVQKYT5V3TlAKEJlRbTMjZ4vPh.jpg","original_title":"Papá Youtuber","original_language":"es"},{"id":52010,"adult":false,"title":"Ultramarines: A Warhammer 40,000 Movie","video":false,"overview":"A squad of Ultramarines answer a distress call from an Imperial Shrine World. A full Company of Imperial Fists was stationed there, but there is no answer from them. The squad investigates to find out what has happened there.","genre_ids":[16,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9549,"vote_count":152,"poster_path":"/eFfkF9uVqOhAxIKEyNCHfRRdGgj.jpg","release_date":"2010-12-10","vote_average":5.832,"backdrop_path":"/oOBtTgunRkq4xKMoe7DrffHpKIf.jpg","original_title":"Ultramarines: A Warhammer 40,000 Movie","original_language":"en"},{"id":498919,"adult":false,"title":"Valentina's Wedding","video":false,"overview":"Valentina's seemingly idyllic life in the US is interrupted when planning a wedding means introducing her fiancé to her scandalous family in Mexico.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3666,"vote_count":66,"poster_path":"/sD6o09KA4KyxWvvB8rKn8bQuuD5.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-09","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/nvSHwiWDU2yX6sNlCiKiGeeiNoW.jpg","original_title":"La Boda de Valentina","original_language":"es"},{"id":554572,"adult":false,"title":"This Is Tomas","video":false,"overview":"Leo and his band decide to bring Thomas to play in a wedding. They have no idea how complex it is to spend a day with someone with autism.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1408,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/2OfdMLI6eQvwGuuc3lBJo5a2nTV.jpg","rele