s lost.\" But, once again, everything becomes complicated, and the excesses are worse than those of long ago.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":0.1668,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/vfiGF0kxAcfMku5zzJVl0E5on70.jpg","release_date":"2012-11-06","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Vicio sangriento","original_language":"es"},{"id":1058612,"adult":false,"title":"Fresh with Fireworks","video":false,"overview":"This story took place in a small Belarusian village at Christmas time. Having received a three-day vacation, Anatoly came here to play a wedding with the beautiful Lyuba. Their relatives take up the preparations and a funny pre-wedding huddle begins....","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.1296,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/vvIwonLAEtZeuyJDNyaawGnZDB0.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/cHVC5FvuLVVW6sxNJMe7Lgdw8Qg.jpg","original_title":"Свежына з салютам","original_language":"be"},{"id":653598,"adult":false,"title":"Spree","video":false,"overview":"Desperate for an online following, a rideshare driver has figured out a deadly plan to go viral and he will stop at nothing to get his five minutes of fame.","genre_ids":[35,80,27,53],"popularity":2.4794,"vote_count":530,"poster_path":"/tbYvzpy4QFhUHRBHe4VeUKJst96.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-14","vote_average":6.399,"backdrop_path":"/2wKOO39vOvWK1vBDb72NuNfkE55.jpg","original_title":"Spree","original_language":"en"},{"id":653606,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Shift","video":false,"overview":"Stanley, an aging fast food worker, prepares to work his final graveyard shift after 38 years. When he's asked to train his replacement, Jevon, Stanley's weekend takes an unexpected turn.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.639,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/76x4TVjygz9t0GG9YLcrmiRck95.jpg","release_date":"2020-09-25","vote_average":5.663,"backdrop_path":"/hUTmShjGZ1dlZyJLxBw9qT3OmEI.jpg","original_title":"The Last Shift","original_language":"en"},{"id":653572,"adult":false,"title":"